Following changes are made to the `data2evidence/logto/Dockerfile` (a slightly modified version of logto/logto Dockerfile).
```
- download the source code of d2e
- replace the to-replace/SignIn/Main.tsx in the path /logto/packages/experience/src/pages/SignIn/Main.tsx
- copy the folder services/alp-logto/connector-alp-azuread
- install and build D2E connector
- link the connector to Logto
```

D2E connector is available alongside other connectors for usage in the admin console. 